Panda (パンダ) is a second year student at Tokyo Prefectural Jujutsu High School who takes part in the Sister School Exchange Event. Although having an appearance of a giant panda, he is actually a unique type of Cursed Corpse created by Masamichi Yaga, the principal of the school, in which not only does Panda have sentience, but grows and matures as he ages. Also unique to him is having three 'cores' (the 'heart' of a Cursed Corpse), which he can change back and forth to unlock various abilities namely a Panda, Gorilla and a Triceratops. During the Sister School Event, he defeats and bonds with Mechamaru. After grieving the death of his creator, Masamichi Yaga, Panda joins the Culling Games with Itadori and Fushiguro in the effort to stop it. Panda engages in a battle with Hajime Kashimo, a resurrected sorcerer from the Heian era, who manages to defeat all of his cores. Only the interference of Kinji Hakari stops Kashimo from killing Panda.
